isoiec80000:term-t7-12-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "luminous energy"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t7-12-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "DEPRECATED: quantity of light"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t7-12-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Q_\"v\""@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t7-12-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "(Q)"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t7-12 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "7-12" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t7-12-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t7-12-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t7-12-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t7-12-1 ;
  skos:definition """energy of electromagnetic waves weighted by the spectral luminous efficiency (<<t7-10.2>>) multiplied by maximum luminous efficacy (<<t7-11.3>>) of a specified photometric condition"""@en ;
  skos:note """Luminous energy for photopic vision is expressed by

[stem%unnumbered]
++++
Q_\"v\" = K_\"m\" int_0^(oo) Q_(\"e\",lambda)(lambda)V(lambda)\"d\"lambda
++++

where stem:[Q_(\"e\",lambda)(lambda)] is the spectral radiant energy (<<t7-2.2>>) at wavelength stem:[lambda] (<<iso80000-3>>), stem:[V(lambda)] is spectral luminous efficiency (<<t7-10.2>>), and stem:[K_\"m\"] is maximum luminous efficacy (<<t7-11.3>>).

Luminous energy can be emitted, transferred or received.

Luminous energy can be expressed by the time integral of the luminous flux (<<t7-13>>), stem:[Phi_\"v\"], over a given duration (<<iso80000-3>>), stem:[Delta t]

[stem%unnumbered]
++++
Q_\"v\" = int_(Delta t) Phi_\"v\" \"d\"t
++++

The corresponding radiometric quantity is \"radiant energy\" (<<t7-2.1>>). The corresponding quantity for photons is \"photon energy\" (<<t7-19.2>>).
"""@en ;
  isoiec80000:hasUnit isoiec80000:unit-lm*s ;
  isoiec80000:hasUnit isoiec80000:unit-cd*sr*s ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-7 .